        </editorialNote><section id="ID_1438402552390_003" name="s1" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2019-04-11" status="operational" temporalId="s1"><num value="1">1.</num><heading>Interpretation</heading><leadIn>In this Order—</leadIn><def name="Company"><term>company</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">公司</term>) means the APT Satellite Company
            Limited.</def></section><section id="ID_1438402552406_002" name="s2" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2019-04-11" status="operational" temporalId="s2"><num value="2">2.</num><heading>Exemption</heading><leadIn>The company, to the extent that it—</leadIn><paragraph id="ID_1438410837967_026" name="a" temporalId="s2_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>establishes or maintains a means of telecommunications; and</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438410837967_034" name="b" temporalId="s2_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>uses or possesses apparatus for telecommunications,</content></paragraph><continued>on the satellite APSTAR-IIR, is exempted from the obligation to hold a licence under <ref>section 8(1)</ref> of the Ordinance.</continued><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/2000/36">36 of 2000 s. 28</ref>)</sourceNote></section></main></subLeg>